de.ovgu.featureide.fm.ui.properties

Class FMPropertyManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ovgu.featureide.fm.ui.properties.FMPropertyManagerDefaults
      • de.ovgu.featureide.fm.ui.properties.FMPropertyManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GUIDefaults

    @CheckReturnValue
public class FMPropertyManager
extends FMPropertyManagerDefaults
implements GUIDefaults
    Manages all persistent properties defined at the property page.
    These properties are defined for the whole workspace.

    Use this methods instead of GUIDefaults.
    Author:
    Jens Meinicke, Marcus Pinnecke
    See Also:
    FMPropertyPage
